{"cid":"1576208565560333","cha_name":"肖战","desc":"肖战，1991年10月5日出生于重庆市，中国内地男演员、歌手。\n2015年，以选手的身份参加浙江卫视才艺养成选秀节目《燃烧吧少年》。2016年4月，主演校园星座超能力网络剧《超星星学园》。2018年4月25日，古装奇幻网络剧《哦！我的皇帝陛下》在腾讯视频播出，肖战凭北堂墨染一角崭露头角。2019年6月27日，领衔主演的古装仙侠剧《陈情令》在腾讯视频播出，肖战凭魏无羡一角赢得广泛关注。7月，主演的古装玄幻剧《斗罗大陆》正式杀青。8月，主演都市情感剧《余生，请多指教》。9月13日，主演的古装仙侠电影《诛仙I》在全国上映。2020年1月24日，肖战首次登上中央广播电视总台春节联欢晚会，与谢娜等合作表演小品《喜欢你，喜欢我》。2月2日，参与演唱的抗疫主题歌曲《坚信爱会赢》及MV正式首发。4月25日零点，歌曲《光点》正式上线。11月19日，参演的古装言情传奇剧《狼殿下》播出，肖战在剧中饰演落拓不羁的赏金猎人疾冲。\n现有待播剧：《余生，请多指教》、《斗罗大陆》。","schema":"aweme://aweme/challenge/detail?cid=1576208565560333","author":{"uid":"6796248446","short_id":"52","nickname":"抖音小助手","gender":1,"signature":"本宝宝暂时还没想到个性签名","avatar_larger":{"uri":"1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p9.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_thumb":{"uri":"100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p9.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_medium":{"uri":"720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p6.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"birthday":"","is_verified":true,"follow_status":0,"aweme_count":0,"following_count":0,"follower_count":0,"favoriting_count":0,"total_favorited":0,"is_block":false,"hide_search":true,"constellation":10,"location":"","hide_location":false,"weibo_verify":"","custom_verify":"","unique_id":"douyin","bind_phone":" {"cid":"1665953433364487","cha_name":"拳皇直播","desc":"美国波士顿，能够进入异次元解封八歧大蛇的三神器八尺琼勾玉、八咫镜和草稚剑正在展出，中情局特工不知火舞正从八神家族传人八神庵处打探三神器的秘密，岂料卢卡尔抢走三神器抢走并躲入了异次元。\n神乐家族传人千鹤透露被抢走的草雉剑为假，委托不知火舞向草稚家族求助。卢卡尔抢走神器后诱骗KOF大赛的格斗家们进入异次元，意欲成为拳皇。\n同时不知火舞和八神庵邀请草稚京一同出战打败卢卡尔。中情局为了调查这起异次元中的犯罪行为亦派出探员特瑞与不知火舞等人一起进入异次元。","schema":"aweme://aweme/challenge/detail?cid=1665953433364487","author":{"uid":"6796248446","short_id":"52","nickname":"抖音小助手","gender":1,"signature":"本宝宝暂时还没想到个性签名","avatar_larger":{"uri":"1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p9.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_thumb":{"uri":"100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p9.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_medium":{"uri":"720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p6.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"birthday":"","is_verified":true,"follow_status":0,"aweme_count":0,"following_count":0,"follower_count":0,"favoriting_count":0,"total_favorited":0,"is_block":false,"hide_search":true,"constellation":10,"location":"","hide_location":false,"weibo_verify":"","custom_verify":"","unique_id":"douyin","bind_phone":"","special_lock":0,"need_recommend":0,"is_binded_weibo":false,"weibo_name":"","weibo_schema":"","weibo_url":"","story_open":false,"story_count":0,"has_facebook_token":false,"has_twitter_token":false,"fb_e
